    "The protocol was registered prospectively with the Open Science Framework (registration https://doi.org/10.17605/OSF.IO/E8ZG7) on October 9, 2023.",
    "Our review focuses on three key questions: (i) In which areas of epidemiological modeling have integrated models been applied?",
    "(ii) What infectious diseases have been modeled using integrated models?",
    "(iii) How have AI techniques and mechanistic epidemiological models been integrated?",
